{"tid":2161132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反了反了】罵習近平「蠢到極點」 中共黨校退休師「嚴重違紀」被開除黨籍","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T16:01:00.000Z","uid":293677,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ff80e29039d5a92d07a4048725ee1fcb47c358","tid":2161132,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3262755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3262755&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21BphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=e5afc421\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3262755&h=74622160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3262755</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-08-17 15:08:43<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國近期內憂外患不斷，境內頻傳「反習」聲浪。日前一段中共中央黨校退休教師蔡霞私下批評習近平、中共體制的錄音檔瘋傳，甚至傳出她曾在一個「紅二代」聚會上，痛斥中國的暴行，並力挺爭議人士。今日中共中央黨校（國家行政學院）宣布，已開除蔡霞的黨籍，並取消所有退休待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">中共中央黨校黨建教研部的退休教師蔡霞，日前傳出私下痛斥習近平無視黨紀國法、隨意制定罪名，讓黨淪為「政治殭屍」，使中共走到窮途末路。相關錄音檔在網上瘋傳，之後又被爆料她曾在一個「紅二代」聚會上，表示自己支持港人擁有治理權，批評中共正在毀壞香港自由貿易港和全球三大金融中心的地位，根本就是「挑戰全球」，尤其與人類文明為敵，批評習近平的行為「蠢到極點」，並力挺批習的北京地產商任志強，狂踩中共、習近平地雷。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對此，中共中央黨校今日宣布該校退休教師蔡霞，因發表有嚴重政治問題和損害國家聲譽的言論，「性質極其惡劣、情節極其嚴重，嚴重違反黨的政治紀律、組織紀律」，被開除中國共產黨黨籍，取消其享受的相關退休待遇，此舉形同證實網上傳言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuOPC7r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuOPC7r.gif&h=ace09e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">包子份人好少氣<br />\n俾人話兩句就發晒爛渣</span>"},{"pid":"77855fb886039c277fba20cd6978fda4c06a57e7","tid":2161132,"uid":293677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">表示自己支持港人擁有治理權，批評中共正在毀壞香港自由貿易港和全球三大金融中心的地位，根本就是「挑戰全球」，尤其與人類文明為敵，批評習近平的行為「蠢到極點」</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5b99ffaaeed9240674d96d6b7f7be837aad4aeca","tid":2161132,"uid":172172,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"退休師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b894882fc62537282ea60224eedb710d3bcfcc","tid":2161132,"uid":191926,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"佢同任志強的共同點<br />\n佢地都係做無實權的虛職<br />\n<br />\n你見到胡德平果班都係  <br />\n基本上投閒置散<br />\n<br />\n有實權的改革派 <br />\n係1989年後被人踢哂出局<br />\n<br />\n1989年後中共權力核心存在改革派<br />\n係嚴重假象<br />\n起碼美國都中左招 十幾年"},{"pid":"7bde0dee531ea1aeb3227dbe6ba9c01714086cbd","tid":2161132,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"留返你條狗命咪算好彩"},{"pid":"33da3b1cac3881d13a26a7f2fd6945ce505eb8a1","tid":2161132,"uid":52146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"人地退休先開除黨籍<br />\n多謝你都嚟唔切啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746d834890452ff71bf5dc28be2ba902f4c0e2e6","tid":2161132,"uid":270730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33da3b1cac3881d13a26a7f2fd6945ce505eb8a1","tid":2161132,"uid":52146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"人地退休先開除黨籍<br />\n多謝你都嚟唔切啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"可以去西方國家申請政治庇護<br 